<page section="download">
  <heading>Download</heading>

  <content>
    <p>
      Go to <github-releases-stable /> and download <strong><csharp-api-download-file /></strong>.
    </p>

    <div id="download-info">
      <img src="img/csharp-api-in-vs.png" class="pic" style="float: right; margin-left: 10px;" alt="Carrot2 C# / .NET API in Visual Studio" />

      <strong>After download completes:</strong>

      <ol>
        <li>
          Extract the archive to some local directory
        </li>

        <li>
          Look in the <tt>examples</tt> directory for code examples
        </li>

        <li>
          See <c2 /> Manual for <manual-link target="_blank" section="section.integration.compiling-csharp-program-with-carrot2">instructions on how 
          to compile a C# with <c2 /></manual-link>.
        </li>
      </ol>

      <p class="note">
        <strong>Note: </strong><c2 /> <csa /> requires .NET Framework version 3.5 or later.
      </p>
    </div>
  </content>
</page>
